Sentencas: Advances in nanotechnology have enabled solid oxide fuel cells to perform high-efficiency energy conversion at lower operating temperatures than before.
Titulo: Effect of Electrolyte Thickness of Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cell on Nanostructure and Performance

Sentencas: In particular, the thin film electrolyte can effectively offset the drop in ion conductivity at a low operating temperature due to a reduced ion path.
Titulo: Effect of Electrolyte Thickness of Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cell on Nanostructure and Performance

Sentencas: In this study, the performance difference of solid oxide fuel cells according to the thickness of these thin film electrolytes was compared.
Titulo: Effect of Electrolyte Thickness of Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cell on Nanostructure and Performance

Sentencas: Thin film solid oxide fuel cells were fabricated with YSZ electrolytes of 3.3 mu m, 4.0 mu m, and 4.7 mu m thickness using different sputtering deposition times.
Titulo: Effect of Electrolyte Thickness of Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cell on Nanostructure and Performance

Sentencas: First, the thickness of the electrolyte affected the gas tightness.
Titulo: Effect of Electrolyte Thickness of Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cell on Nanostructure and Performance

Sentencas: The OCV of the cell using the 3.3 mu m, 4.0 mu m, and 4.7 mu m thick electrolyte showed 1.01 V, 1.03 V and 1.05 V respectively.
Titulo: Effect of Electrolyte Thickness of Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cell on Nanostructure and Performance

Sentencas: As the sputter deposition time increased, the surface grain size of the YSZ electrolyte also increased, affecting both the electrolyte's ohmic and the electrode's polarization resistance.
Titulo: Effect of Electrolyte Thickness of Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cell on Nanostructure and Performance

Sentencas: Therefore, the difference in the thickness of the electrolyte showed a dramatic difference in performance.
Titulo: Effect of Electrolyte Thickness of Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cell on Nanostructure and Performance

Sentencas: The cells with 3.3 mu m, 4.0 mu m, and 4.7 mu m thick electrolytes showed performances of 193 mW/cm2, 99 mW/cm2, and 57 mW/cm2, respectively at 500 degrees C.
Titulo: Effect of Electrolyte Thickness of Thin Film Solid Oxide Fuel Cell on Nanostructure and Performance
